title: allow us to reintroduce ourselves
itunes:title: allow us to reintroduce ourselves
description:
Brooke and Danielle are alone this week to REINTRODUCE themselves!  Gals on the Go has been a show for over 2 years now and the gals have experienced a lot of growth and change in that time.  In this episode, the gals talk about where they are from, how they ended up at the same school, and how they became friends back in 2013.
